title: What AIR can I expect with 523 in the NEET 2019, considering the fact that the paper was easy? - Quora
tags: Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery Degrees

response.answer_text: As the paper was easy and the number of candidates have increased this year the ranks are definitely going to hike up. As everyone is expecting the cut off to increase by 20–30 marks I am considering the same. So last year for 500 marks the rank was around 20,000 . So I think that for 520 marks this year the rank can be between 20–25k.

Thanks for A2A With 523 marks according to NEET 2017 it can be some AIR 16K-18K. But you just can't stick on to that. Get ready to face anything. If there are huge no of students getting great scores like 660+ then you can't stick on to that :) Shaun
